# Claude Code — shared config is tracked (settings.json, agents/); local state is not.
# Verified 2026-07-16 against real artifacts, not a template:
#   settings.local.json  — personal overrides
#   scheduled_tasks.lock — runtime lock (sessionId/pid)
#   worktrees/           — where EnterWorktree puts isolated worktrees. Untracked
#                          without this, so a stray `git add -A` could commit a
#                          whole worktree. Verified: it was NOT ignored before.
# Session todos are NOT here — they live in ~/.claude/projects/<path>/<session-id>/.
# A `.claude/todos/` rule was ignoring a path that has never existed in any repo.
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
.claude/worktrees/

